                <h1><img src="../../images/_gear.png" height="40" width="40" alt="">Is There a Culture of Bigotry and Violence in Islam?</h1>
                <h4 class="author"><img src="../../images/_long_line.jpg" height="1" width="1075" alt="">By Faysal Burhan</h4>
              </div>
