<h3>Wahhabists Responsible for the Destruction of Syria</h3>
<p>Intolerance and hate by extremists does not stop at breeding hatred only, such as that between Muslims (certain groups) and Coptic Christians of Egypt but much worse. The twisted creed of Wahhbism permitted them to even carry actual wars against other Muslims. By labeling Shia and Sufi Muslims as heretics, permission is granted to kill, even though they are believers in Allah (SWT) and His Prophet (p).
</p>
<p>A recent victim of the Salafi/Wahhabi perverted creed is Syria. Syria is a moderate state, where Muslims, Christians and Jews lived in peace for centuries. But since Syria allied with Iran, the Shia state, this became a pinching nerve to Saudi Arabia and Qatar. Therefore, <a href="http://www.democracynow.org/2013/3/15/2_years_after_invasion_to_crush">they infiltrated the Syrian crisis, poured the fuels of rancor,</a> urging the Syrians to revolt against their “infidel Alawi” government. <a href="http://article.wn.com/view/2013/02/26/Saudi_Arabia_Arming_Syrian_Rebels_With_Croatian_Weapons_Sinc/">They supplied the conflict with outside jihadists, and supported the Syrian rebels with arms and money.</a> Another reference for Saudi Arabia arms Syrian rebels via Jordan.</p> 
